text:
4 storey building. Bottom 2 floors are shops while third floor are 2 storey flats. Building looks dated.

Specialised shops here like veterinary, pet groomer, music shop, massage parlour, dentist, clinic, cheese shop etc.

Across the street there are more neighbourhood shops so this building offers different amenities to the area.

Some parking lots right in front of the building.

Usually not a busy place as people come over for a specific shop and will not loiter for long.

A lower rise commercial and shophouses building along Jalan Jurong Kechil (diagonally across Esso station).
(Last update/ review Feb2017)
Da Capo Music Academy has a lovely guitar teacher called Andy. Patient and encouraging.
